title: Welcome to the Team - Chris Joslin
description:
Arnette welcomes Chris Joslin to the team with a tour around San Diego's local skateparks, where we ran into Pat Duffy and Willy Santos.
On location at Arnette HQ, Rancho Penasquitos, Prince Park and Alga Norte.
